seminar. Dette års seminar vil foregår på Skarrildhus, Danmark 7.-9. maj 2014. Vi byder alle interesserede forskere velkomne til at ansøge om deltagelse i seminaret. JOURNAL OF SCANDINAVIAN STUDIES IN CRIMINOLOGY 16/08/10 Published in cooperation between NSfK, the Crime Preventive Councils in Denmark, Finland and Norway, and the Department of Criminology, Stockholm University. The Journal is published by Taylor & Francis and edited by Janne Kivivuori. Latest issue NORDISK TIDSSKRIFT FOR KRIMINALVIDENSKAB 16/08/10 Thomas Elholm, redaktør. Særnummer om miljøstrafferet. Artiklerne er skrevet af en arbejdsgruppe under NSfK. Latest issue ABOUT THE COUNCIL Introduction Executive Secretary Council members Contact Secretaries Contact info Annual Reports Purpose and Statutes News RESEARCH Current Research Projects Completed Research Projects Conferences and Seminars Grants PUBLICATIONS Newsletter Research Seminar Reports Contact Seminar Reports Annual Reports Other Reports Bibliography_Older BIBLIOGRAPHY Thesaurus Author Databases Links Biblio siteindex LINKS Denmark Finland Greenland Iceland Norway Sweden Other links 2010 Scandinavian Research Council for Criminology c/o Faculty of Law - Aarhus Universitet | Bartholins All 16 - Building 1328 | 8000 Aarhus C - Denmark | +45 87165487 
